    <p class="max2 flex justify-center items-center translate-y-[-10px] text-3xl px-28 leading-[50px] right-0 text-center text-black/80">The Government Recycling Reward Program encourages people to recycle by offering 1 INR per point for submitting plastic, paper, and other waste at collection centers. This initiative helps keep the environment clean while rewarding participants.

